item.title: Speaker - XConf-2021 - Thoughtworks India
item.description: The XConf XConf is Thoughtworks annual technology event created by technologists. It is designed for technologists who care deeply about software and its impact on the world. This year, XConf will be a virtual experience available at two different time slots. October 7th and 8th will feature pre-recorded sessions and October 9th will feature live sessions. During the nine exciting talks spread across three days. I am exited to sharing the stage with renowned technologists like Neal Ford, Dr.
